00:01:13.019 --> 00:01:15.139
that we would be a good soldier,

00:01:15.139 --> 00:01:18.019
not simply being content with the reality

00:01:18.019 --> 00:01:19.220
that we are soldiers.

00:01:19.220 --> 00:01:21.199
