00:01:22.739 --> 00:01:24.620
you were enlisted into the army of God

00:01:24.620 --> 00:01:26.819
and you are a soldier of God.

00:01:26.819 --> 00:01:28.779
But we've had the opportunity as we've studied

00:01:28.779 --> 00:01:30.139
through this portion of scripture

00:01:30.139 --> 00:01:33.139
to understand that the Lord tells us

00:01:33.139 --> 00:01:37.260
that there's this phrase of being a good soldier,

00:01:37.260 --> 00:01:40.699
not just being a soldier, but being a good soldier.

00:01:40.699 --> 00:01:43.139
And we've noted four characteristics

00:01:43.139 --> 00:01:45.180
over the past four messages.

00:01:45.180 --> 00:01:47.019
And we said this from verse number three,

00:01:47.019 --> 00:01:50.459
that a good soldier endures hardness.

00:01:50.459 --> 00:01:52.400
There'll be opposition, there'll be difficulty.

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:56.059
I said this, that a soldier is a soldier

00:01:56.059 --> 00:01:58.779
and some people have had the idea

00:01:58.779 --> 00:02:01.339
that they wanna be a soldier, but they don't want conflict.

00:02:01.339 --> 00:02:03.099
