00:02:03.099 --> 00:02:03.980
they don't want battle,

00:02:03.980 --> 00:02:06.339
but the soldier of the Lord Jesus Christ,

00:02:06.339 --> 00:02:09.580
we understand that we are engaged in spiritual battle,

00:02:09.580 --> 00:02:13.880
spiritual warfare, and we need to endure hardness.

00:02:13.880 --> 00:02:15.460
We said this, that a good soldier,

00:02:15.460 --> 00:02:16.899
according to verse number four,

00:02:16.899 --> 00:02:19.979
he avoids distractions.

00:02:19.979 --> 00:02:22.759
And oh, is it not true that the distractions abound?

00:02:22.759 --> 00:02:24.300
The enemy wants us to be distracted

00:02:24.300 --> 00:02:28.020
