00:03:31.279 --> 00:03:32.839
You can't please everyone.

00:03:32.839 --> 00:03:36.619
But I found that instead of trying to please people,

00:03:36.619 --> 00:03:39.199
to please the crowds, the masses,

00:03:39.199 --> 00:03:42.759
that if we can just live our lives to please the Lord,

00:03:42.759 --> 00:03:45.320
because the reality is that it's so much more important

00:03:45.320 --> 00:03:46.839
that God is pleased with us

00:03:46.839 --> 00:03:49.240
than that the people are pleased with us.

00:03:49.320 --> 00:03:51.839
And we must live with that understanding.

