00:06:28.660 --> 00:06:30.720
And so as we come to this thought this morning,

00:06:30.720 --> 00:06:32.179
if you're taking notes, number one,

00:06:32.179 --> 00:06:36.339
I want you to consider the exhortation to work hard.

00:06:36.339 --> 00:06:37.820
We find that throughout the scriptures

00:06:37.820 --> 00:06:40.459
that God gives us the exhortation,

00:06:40.459 --> 00:06:41.980
he exhorts us, he instructs us,

00:06:41.980 --> 00:06:43.739
he commands us to work hard.

00:06:43.739 --> 00:06:47.220
We live, I believe today, that we live in a time

00:06:47.220 --> 00:06:51.260
