00:07:18.399 --> 00:07:22.320
and they've not learned how to develop a good work ethic.

00:07:22.320 --> 00:07:24.839
And we find that the Bible would instruct us,

00:07:24.839 --> 00:07:28.679
exhort us to be hard workers, to work hard for the Lord.

00:07:28.679 --> 00:07:33.679
The lack of a good work ethic in our society,

00:07:33.799 --> 00:07:37.940
